articles.title: About this blog
articles.contents:
These blog posts record my projects and assignments of Visualization Analytics and Application course during the learning journey of Master of IT in Business (MITB) in Singapore Management University.
I mainly used the R and Tableau to build this website and finish the assignments.
Hope you can enjoying them!
You can contact me at zhen.li.2020@mitb.smu.edu.sg .
